{"tid":1243317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"單手盾控或成今META最大贏家?","createTime":"2019-06-19T11:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T14:11:11.000Z","uid":180561,"like":16,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e96f083e2f185c133bba8c5003910a70fbd73e5b","tid":1243317,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:51:06.000Z","msg":"首先多謝巴打 HcDElias#141072 既激勵，令小弟衝出CD-ROM<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242880/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242880/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我一直都好愛呢隻GAME, 佢帶俾我太多回憶, 太多好既時光, 我唔想望住佢咁樣死, 特此譔文.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lolskinshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Khazix_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flolskinshop.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2FKhazix_1.jpg&h=c9faadb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://lolskinshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Trundle_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flolskinshop.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2FTrundle_4.jpg&h=d561dea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">此文只討論坦角出裝,  SUP角, 後排不在此討論</span><br />\n<br />\n係而家呢個META最多出現既係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">速龍卡力斯、全坦特朗普</span></span>等大男衝排角，我認為最好既Counter配置係<span style=\"color: red;\">蘭盾配噴漆</span>等控場道具<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZj6hZi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZj6hZi.png&h=2a927128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前排坦 當然配蘭盾 但係再配個遮我覺得冇咩用 正如你4000血300物防再加件好戰者效果唔大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果盾+噴漆，就可以有防有控場!<br />\n<br />\n坦角冇控場就係捱打，防會破、血會扣，亦因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地個陣唔會有輸出角</span></span> 唯有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">控場</span></span>技能/道具令對方失去戰鬥能力係上策, 例如致盲/倒地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://apollo-pbe-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/1407925145512/Screen12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapollo-pbe-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com%2F1407925145512%2FScreen12.png&h=5dc16491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前排控場角冇坦度，就係被秒送水餃。<span style=\"color: red;\">噴完一秒就黑Mon</span>，無法成功致盲，等返幾碌先可以重生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前排控場角增加坦度可以大大增加被衝鋒時間，控場技能可以有更大時間發揮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/9.12.1/img/item/3143.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fddragon.leagueoflegends.com%2Fcdn%2F9.12.1%2Fimg%2Fitem%2F3143.png&h=676f629d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/9.12.1/img/item/3030.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fddragon.leagueoflegends.com%2Fcdn%2F9.12.1%2Fimg%2Fitem%2F3030.png&h=62436389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由此，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蘭盾+致盲噴漆係我諗到最好既前排單兵裝備</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mobafire.com/images/avatars/garen-classic.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobafire.com%2Fimages%2Favatars%2Fgaren-classic.png&h=b1ea9c58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mobafire.com/images/champion/square/teemo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobafire.com%2Fimages%2Fchampion%2Fsquare%2Fteemo.png&h=81806d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一個方法係全坦角+提摩, 前坦後控, 但係機動性太低, 變相二人三足, 亦需要時間磨合, 否則出現你衝我退 我衝你退情況出現咁就仆街喇. 大家都係單排玩街場多, 我建議D簡單唔需要高默契既玩法會比較易. <br />\nP.S. 強調!我並唔係話英雄主義單兵上場, 團隊合作都係十分重要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://exp.gg/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/4-36x36.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexp.gg%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F4-36x36.gif&h=750703be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://exp.gg/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/4-36x36.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexp.gg%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F4-36x36.gif&h=750703be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://exp.gg/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/4-36x36.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexp.gg%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F4-36x36.gif&h=750703be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://exp.gg/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/4-36x36.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexp.gg%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F4-36x36.gif&h=750703be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://exp.gg/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/4-36x36.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexp.gg%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F4-36x36.gif&h=750703be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://exp.gg/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/4-36x36.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexp.gg%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F4-36x36.gif&h=750703be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n21號呢場分區決賽 唔好再拎6多蘭盾出嚟喇please 再送頭只會滾雪球，哂大家時間，到時真係FF20投<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">P.P.S.另外, 有D中意既IDEA, 例如水桶Q技 秒破解葛雷夫Q催淚彈=緩速+黑mon, 呢D正野覺得有用既 唔好淨係LIKE 要放上戰場先有用,紙上談兵就收得皮喇</span>"},{"pid":"36ada1ce0adb9011e978d62bf20d5a9b907d2f52","tid":1243317,"uid":180561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:51:23.000Z","msg":"SOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />PO錯台"},{"pid":"f80eaa6e52a38bfa4f3709b5664656bb47b78022","tid":1243317,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"盾裝分享<br />\n<br />\n保我命3000<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1579306826/videos/10213589037871823/?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1579306826%2Fvideos%2F10213589037871823%2F%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyuyMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=1b88979b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1579306826/videos/10213589037871823/?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n紙皮A盾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuYF65e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuYF65e.jpg&h=9f46779f&s={SIZE}